message.content:
Genetic Algorithms, Rule Learning. 

Genetic Algorithms are the main focus of the paper, as the authors explore the application of GAs to a symbolic learning task. The GA concept learner (GABL) is implemented and compared to an incremental concept learner, ID5R. 

Rule Learning is also relevant, as the GABL is a rule-based learner that learns a concept from a set of positive and negative examples. The authors note that GABL is effective and competitive with ID5R as the target concept increases in complexity.
